content.rendered:
BOSS AIR STREET CRUISER AIRFORCE

Boss Air Street Cruiser Airforce available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

This kit is an air package ideal for Lowriders, Mini trucks, and all other air suspension installs.

Using 2 of Boss Air’s PX06 12volt 1.8cfm 100% Duty Cycle Air Compressors for rapid refilling the 9 port tank ready for the next use.

Includes;

  • 2 x PX-06 12volt 100% Duty, 1.8cfm Air Compressors
  • 1 x AT-05  5 port Boss Aluminium Air Tank
  • 1 x 110-150psi Pressure Switch
  • 2 x Check Valves
  • 2 x Braided Hoses
  • 1 x Brass 1/4″ Bung
  • 1 x Drain Tap
  • Instruction Sheet
To view the range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
